<heading id="D0A74D612179FF8A66CBE7E7006C8402" box="[929,1335,1779,1803]" centered="true" fontSize="10" level="2" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A66CBE7E7006C8402" bold="true" box="[929,1335,1779,1803]" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
Key to 
<collectingRegion id="499434EF2179FF8A6699E7E7010D8403" box="[1011,1110,1779,1802]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C50818E2179FF8A61A5E7E0006C8402" authorityName="Erichson" authorityYear="1845" box="[1231,1335,1780,1803]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A61A5E7E0006C8402" bold="true" box="[1231,1335,1780,1803]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">Baeocera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C34AA9862179FF8A6656E63600C78B10" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" type="key">
<keyStep id="30A4E2A82179FF8A6656E63600C78B10" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
<paragraph id="8BEFFA0D2179FF8A6656E63600C78493" blockId="1.[828,1437,1826,2074]" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
<keyLead id="30A159382179FF8A6656E63600C78493" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
1. Body length about 
<quantity id="4CA857E82179FF8A6141E63601248430" box="[1067,1151,1826,1850]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" unit="mm" value="1.1">1.1 mm</quantity>
. Antennomere VI about as wide as antennomere IV. Elytra lacking basal striae. Lateral parts of metaventrite coarsely punctate. .......... ........................................... 
<taxonomicName id="4C50818E2179FF8A6118E69600C78493" authority="Lobl, 1983" authorityName="Lobl" authorityYear="1983" box="[1138,1436,1922,1946]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="derougemonti">
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A6118E696007D8493" bold="true" box="[1138,1318,1922,1946]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">B. derougemonti</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC187FC2179FF8A6047E69600C78493" author="LOBL I." box="[1325,1436,1922,1946]" firstAuthor="Lobl" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen der Schweizerischen Entomologischen Gesellschaft" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" pagination="285 - 293" part="56" refId="ref12872" refString="LOBL I. 1983: Sechs neue Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) von Sulawesi, Indonesien. Mitteilungen der Schweizerischen Entomologischen Gesellschaft 56: 285 - 293." title="Sechs neue Scaphidiidae (Coleoptera) von Sulawesi, Indonesien" type="journal article" year="1983">Löbl, 1983</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEFFA0D2179FF8A6656E6B700C78B10" blockId="1.[828,1437,1826,2074]" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
<keyLead id="30A159382179FF8A6656E6B700C78B10" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A6656E6B7061284B3" box="[828,841,1955,1978]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">‒</emphasis>
Body length about 
<quantity id="4CA857E82179FF8A6128E6B601D184B0" box="[1090,1162,1954,1977]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
. Antennomere VI much wider than antennomere IV. Elytra with entire basal striae. Lateral parts of metaventrite appearing impunctate. .......................................... 
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A61ADE91700C78B10" bold="true" box="[1223,1436,2050,2074]" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">
<taxonomicName id="4C50818E2179FF8A61ADE917001B8B10" authority="Löbl, 2018" authorityName="Löbl" authorityYear="2018" box="[1223,1344,2050,2074]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inoptata" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B924261F2179FF8A61ADE917001B8B10" bold="true" box="[1223,1344,2050,2074]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="152">B. inoptata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2179B642179FF8A602DE91600C78B10" box="[1351,1436,2050,2073]" pageId="1" pageNumber="152" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
